      "short": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.XrBOn1MueVB4u5sV]{Nanocyte Knack}</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Your nanites capably innovate new features when you manifest nanite weapons. Choose two of the following special weapon properties: block, bright, deflect</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 5pt;\">AR</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, feint</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 5pt;\">AR</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, grapple, harrying</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 5pt;\">AR</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, penetrating, stun, sunder, or trip. Each time you form a weapon using your gear array, you can apply one of the selected special weapon properties to that weapon. You can select this knack multiple times; each time, select two additional special weapon properties and add them to the list of available properties (you still apply only one at a time).</span></p>",
